== Births ==
== Deaths == * In the 13th year of the Eishō era ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1516]] [[:en:December 1|December 1]]) – Utsunomiya Naritsuna, a Sengoku daimyo and the 17th head of the Utsunomiya clan of Shimotsuke Province, regarded as the restorer of the Utsunomiya clan (born 1468).
